{"tid":2068391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"甩P牌","createTime":"2020-06-17T15:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T10:47:31.000Z","uid":332769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"49ab33307a009e59b8fe084d2cce3cca63f7c0cd","tid":2068391,"uid":332769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:50:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8BivpS9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8BivpS9.jpg&h=9498b4ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有一日就成功甩p牌"},{"pid":"86491c191b4f0acc67707aa3c8d9e4af8fe033bb","tid":2068391,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:51:33.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"c683081fd0b43dda334595a0b052ae487fa98454","tid":2068391,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"傻啦"},{"pid":"429ce96bb4306634009b026010d25cb00d6f93d1","tid":2068391,"uid":314556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T10:47:31.000Z","msg":"我271日都仲未甩p"}]}